name: bab3l's Github
body:
### bab3l's Corner

I play around with GIS toolkits, embedded systems and monitoring/automation architectures to make my day job easier. Most of my repos are private for now, but after a little polish should be public in October 2014. Mostly a mish-mash of Python, C#, C++ and Matlab - brace for the spaghetti code.

If messages don't work, I can usually be found on [my twitter.](http://twitter.com/caveofbabel)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
